the displayed finite lower bound on `mu` is supplied. -/
theorem partialDiagonalWeight_increment_le_of_mu_activity
    (n : Nat) (u k ell : I -> Nat) (i : I) (xi : I -> Real)
    (hprofile : IsPartialSubprofile k ell)
